description: This file defines React components for a Card UI element, including Card, CardHeader, and CardBody, used for building card layouts with styled sections.

methods.name: Card
methods.description: A React functional component that renders a styled container div with optional additional classes, representing a UI card.

methods.name: CardHeader
methods.description: A React functional component that renders a header section for the card with title, optional subtitle, and action elements.

methods.name: CardBody
methods.description: A React functional component that renders the main content area of the card with padding.
